 успешно участие на Startup Bulgaria!</span></span></span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"></span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🙌\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tfd/1/16/1f64c.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span>&nbsp;От 8 до 10 ноември в&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">София</span></span>&nbsp;се проведе тридневното събитие&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">Startup Bulgaria</span></span>. Гордост е да споделим, че част от членовете на&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">робо клуб \"Хелиос\"</span></span>&nbsp;бяха сред участниците,&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">благодарение</span></span>&nbsp;на подкрепата на фирма \"<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">Ардес</span></span>\" и&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">училищното настоятелство</span></span>&nbsp;на СУ \"Л.&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">Каравелов</span></span>\".</span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"></span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"💼\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/td/1/16/1f4bc.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span>&nbsp;Специални благодарности на&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">г-н</span></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">Димитър Димитров</span></span>, управител и собственик на \"<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">Ардес</span></span>\", който, вдъхновен от проектите на робо клуб \"<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">Хелиос</span></span>\", осигури&nbsp;<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">спонсорството</span></span>, за да могат младите таланти да продължат да се развиват и да следват мечтите си напред!</span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"></span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🤖\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t36/1/16/1f916.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span>&nbsp;На събитието присъстваха над 2000 души – предприемачи, млади хора, студенти, ученици и бизнес ангели. Програмата включваше 50 сесии, 7 уъркшопа и 1 хекатон, което направи участието на клуба изключително интересно и полезно за всички!</span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"></span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"><span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🙏\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t80/1/16/1f64f.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span>&nbsp;Ардес ни се довери. Доверете се и Вие!</span></span></span></div></div>',NULL,NULL,1,'2024-11-12 22:00:00','2025-05-06 23:21:18'),(21,1,1,NULL,NULL,'uploads/2024/11/t1/803415477_466136177_8900938716629252_5149526092552722568_n.jpg',NULL,119,'Когато Bosch се довери на Хелиос','kogato-bosch-se-doveri-na-xelios','<div class=\"xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t8c/1/16/1f389.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span> Bosch направи дарение на СУ \"Л. Каравелов\" на стойност над 8000 лв.!</div></div><div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🥇\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t94/1/16/1f947.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span> Робо клуб \"Хелиос\" участваха на националния форум по роботика Para Robotics, където спечелиха първото място с проекта CleanBot и привлякоха вниманието на международната компания Bosch. </div></div><div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🙏\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t80/1/16/1f64f.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span> Дарението включва Ардуино и Микробит китове, мишки роботи, дремели, мултимери, винтоверти, свредла, станции за горещ въздух и още много полезно оборудване!</div></div><div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🔧\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t52/1/16/1f527.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span> <span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><a tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-a xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"color: rgb(56, 88, 152); cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"></a></span>Робо клуб \"Хелиос\" към СУ \"Л. Каравелов\" изказва огромна благодарност на Bosch за високата оценка!</div></div><div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🔹\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf3/1/16/1f539.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span> Bosch ни се довери. Доверете се и вие!</div></div>',NULL,NULL,1,'2024-11-07 22:00:00','2025-05-06 04:43:24'),(22,1,1,NULL,NULL,'uploads/2024/11/t1/910363638_464969993_8836242469765544_1140062742992653679_n.jpg',NULL,200,'На участие във втората конференция \"Училище за успех\"','na-ucastie-viev-vtorata-konferenciia-ucilishhe-za-uspex','<div class=\"xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🌟\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/te0/1/16/1f31f.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span> На 26.10.2024 г. СУ \"Л. Каравелов\" участва във втората конференция \"Училище за успех\", организирана от ИКТ Клъстер - Варна! <span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🌟\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/te0/1/16/1f31f.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span></div></div><div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Г-жа Светла Иванова (директор) и г-н Мартин Петров (ръководител на<b> робоклуб \"Хелиос\")</b> представиха HFEEDER - първата хранилка и поилка в света с изкуствен интелект! <span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🤖\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t36/1/16/1f916.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"💧\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t42/1/16/1f4a7.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span></div></div><div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Над 100 учители споделиха своя опит и идеи за вдъхновяване на децата и за подобряване на учебния процес. <span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"🎓\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t25/1/16/1f393.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"✨\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf4/1/16/2728.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span></div></div><div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><a tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-a xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"color: rgb(56, 88, 152); cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"></a></span>Поздравления на всички участници и на нашите ученици за страхотната работа и представените проекти! <span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"👏\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tfe/1/16/1f44f.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span><span class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\" style=\"text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1px; display: inline-flex; vertical-align: middle; width: 16px; height: 16px; font-family: inherit;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"👏\" class=\"xz74otr\" referrerpolicy=\"origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tfe/1/16/1f44f.png\" style=\"border: 0px; object-fit: fill;\"></span></div></div><div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Вярваме, че заедно – учители, родители, бизнес и администрация – можем да