одина с участие в престижното изложение \"<span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"html-strong xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1s688f\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px;\">Техностарт\" в град Варна</span></span>.</span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"></span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\">Нашите млади таланти имаха честта да представят три иновативни проекта, които вече са се увенчали с успех на национални олимпиади и състезания, печелейки призови места. Тези проекти не само демонстрират техническите умения на учениците, но и тяхната креативност и стремеж към създаване на решения за реалния свят.</span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\"></span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x10flsy6 x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.3333; color: var(--primary-text); min-width: 0px;\">Ето и проектите, които впечатлиха всички присъстващи:</span></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 8, 9); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1e56ztr\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; fon